title: ajc outjar command does not include MANIFEST.MF file
description: When using the `ajc outjar` command, the resulting jar file does not include the `MANIFEST.MF` file even if it exists in the `META-INF` directory.
OB: Currently, when using the `ajc outjar` command, the resulting jar file does not contain the `MANIFEST.MF` file.
EB: The `ajc outjar` command should include the `MANIFEST.MF` file in the resulting jar file if it exists in the `META-INF` directory.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Create a `MANIFEST.MF` file in the `META-INF` directory.
2. Run the `ajc outjar` command to create a jar file.
3. Verify that the resulting jar file does not contain the `MANIFEST.MF` file.
